rComments: He will give the exact same comment for all your essays but your grades will be different. He cannot control class discussion and those teacher's pets sometimes take 30 mins of class time saying things that aren't useful. a nice guy though...

He gives you the same comments on all 3 essays... but then he gives you good grades. If you wanna grade, take him. If you wanna learn, don't. If you are teacher's pet and love talking in class, this is your prof. He almost never stops anybody no matter how off the topic they are.
